data.title: The Penguins of Madagascar S01E03 Ending Credits
data.meta_description: The Penguins Of Madagascar S01E03 Ending Credits - Free download as Powerpoint Presentation (.ppt / .pptx), PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. This document lists the credits for the production and post-production staff of the animated television specials "Kaboom And Kabust" and "The Helmet". It includes the supervising producer, animation producers, directors, voice actors, designers, animators, engineers, editors and other personnel across multiple departments and studios involved in the creation and finishing of the projects.
